General.Name: Hainan Manaslu Acquisition Corp.
General.Description: As of August 17, 2023, Hainan Manaslu Acquisition Corp. was acquired by Able View Inc. in a reverse merger transaction. Hainan Manaslu Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It intends to acquire assets and businesses through a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combinations. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Haikou, China.
General.Address: West Tower, Guorui Building, Haikou, China, 570203
